      "content": "wait sorry \"eyeballs of your muscle fibers\"? i think u might have a typo there lol. what did u mean by that? also can u go a bit deeper into how the cells actually sense that tension? like is there a specific mechanism that converts the physical stretch into those chemical signals?",
